{"tid":1233121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急）求下現場既大家千祈唔好衝","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:39:11.000Z","uid":135852,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7c33f456defed6e97ed87299347f29f57aa34ee3","tid":1233121,"uid":135852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"首先而家凌晨冇議員冇記者，被人打被人砌生豬肉都冇證據幫到你<br />\n<br />\n在場既仲有好多人因為宗教原因留守，呢啲人都唔會選擇去衝<br />\n<br />\n立法會宜家冇人，被你衝入去又點？等被黑警包圍再一口氣拉返去？何況已經講左聽日同星期二休會<br />\n<br />\n夜晚冇開會，你地衝既行動好難得到其他香港人認同，何況而家衝亦都對釋放義士冇幫助 反而俾政府更多理由去定義我地係暴亂<br />\n<br />\n求下你地 唔想再見到人失去前途<br />\n有咩事 日光日白再處理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2072db7dac8c55b4a31b8a2e0ad6ed50fd7d9f9e","tid":1233121,"uid":126736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1866a3a0e1bc0a1d71e398fdf16dc477fd498576","tid":1233121,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:32:06.000Z","msg":"各位要好好保護自己"},{"pid":"bd6259027da82097626240a05e976c0518480208","tid":1233121,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8715b0b030142c3bf84c4b82bccb5a663807a1ff","tid":1233121,"uid":156461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5e4d0b11e40be4b8b3e16ceb3c192c97555610b2","tid":1233121,"uid":156461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"唔係叫大家唔好衝，但時間真係好重要<br />\n衝係要爭取，唔係只係為咗壯烈犧牲！！"},{"pid":"cb8e2da0e3f375c94ae91e5aad7cb6c5fca8df17","tid":1233121,"uid":165421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日同星期二唔撚係休會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f32461c72dd3914888957a67c214706d3fb9ddaa","tid":1233121,"uid":135852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"不受傷不流血不被捕呀！！<br />\n俾鄺神休息唔好要佢擔心呀！！"},{"pid":"49b5bc000cdcecf2da57ecce601e24b74f195dfe","tid":1233121,"uid":156461,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"如果冇計劃咁衝<br />\n大家一齊俾人拉晒，剩低嘅人又人人自危唔敢出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我哋對得住烈士咩？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n一再強調: 唔係叫大家一直和理非非！！<br />\n但呢一刻衝入立法會實在係冇用(一個已經話左比大家聽幾時先有用) 。地鐵收晒，義士亦冇支援<br />\n分分鐘黑警扮守晤住，放晒你哋入去再一網打盡<br />\n各位義士唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cad49e1106b379cd3cc9693a0fb8008a5477ff4","tid":1233121,"uid":174607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"無人衝 純粹等聽日直接三罷"},{"pid":"68336f97273592f4bf231afea4aa8d58b02225ba","tid":1233121,"uid":146982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"095a227b935a55d96febd1e7f5e1f1b8a94395ea","tid":1233121,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61da5c540d67355d2fd05efd494e141616672135","tid":1233121,"uid":135852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8e2da0e3f375c94ae91e5aad7cb6c5fca8df17","tid":1233121,"uid":165421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日同星期二唔撚係休會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"Sorry記錯你屌我啦<br />\n但咩事都好唔好宜家衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd32423141